results.title: Spider-Man: No Way Home
results.overview: Peter Parker is unmasked and no longer able to separate his normal life from the high-stakes of being a superhero.

results.title: Black Panther: Wakanda Forever
results.overview: Queen Ramonda, Shuri, M’Baku and the Dora Milaje fight to protect their nation from intervening world powers in the wake of King T’Challa’s death.

results.title: Avatar: The Way of Water
results.overview: Jake Sully lives with his newfound family formed on the planet of Pandora. Once a familiar threat returns, he must fight a difficult war to protect their people.
